data.description: Welcome to your Beach house! This Charming home is nestled between the river and the ocean in beautiful Ormond Beach. This 3 bedroom 1.5 bathroom home features an open concept with kitchen over looking the enclosed Florida Room for extra space. Fenced-in back yard with plenty of space to entertain. Located a short distance from the ocean and shopping center.Square footage received from tax rolls. All information recorded in the MLS intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
